{"tid":1804571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[交差餉12-2019]自製eBanking $1攬炒機械人","createTime":"2019-12-31T05:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T06:36:01.000Z","uid":261067,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"587494e9aa2e4bc3d96f7d0564e2f1fb194cd82d","tid":1804571,"uid":261067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:39:34.000Z","msg":"年尾收到差餉，好鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但PPS $1攬炒機械人每日只可交3次，已經唔用得。<br />\n<br />\n1個月前有巴打提到可以用eBanking+Mouse Record software交：<br />\n$1攬炒交稅機械人 mid-term成續表已出...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686879/page/20\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686879/page/20</a><br />\n<br />\n我親身試左係work 既。如果你用windows，可跟以下教學：<br />\n1. Install Macro Recorder <a href=\"https://www.jitbit.com/macro-recorder/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jitbit.com%2Fmacro-recorder%2F&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=eedfe6d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jitbit.com/macro-recorder/</a><br />\n或者其他可以錄低Mouse Motion 既software<br />\n2. 預備你的eBanking Account (e.g. HSBC / Hang Seng)<br />\n3. 設定繳費範本 (Hang Seng Bank 有)<br />\n4. Login eBanking &gt; 範本 (Hang Seng) / 繳付賬單(HSBC)<br />\n5. 固定eBanking window 係特定位置, 如maximize / 靠右等, 把scroll bar 拉到最上(以免走位)<br />\n6. 開Macro Record，按&quot;Record&quot; button 開始錄<br />\n7. 用Mouse 去eBanking window做繳費動作，即選商戶/輸入$1/確定交費<br />\n8. 回到最初繳費的頁面<br />\n9. 返去Macro Record，按&quot;Stop&quot; button 停止錄<br />\n10. 將&quot;Repeat&quot; 中的1 改為10 (免費version 最多係10)<br />\n11. 按&quot;Play&quot; button 重複交10次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩唔明白可留言討論交流一下。"},{"pid":"48593c3d31a7efa0549add5179eeaeb6eff21b91","tid":1804571,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:39:52.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署 </ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=fd2b4182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=a6dd11c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">最後一日</span></span><br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要23000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=d3ad85ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">3/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要5000人 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=50e87da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a>"},{"pid":"fb951d1694f1d35aa300c2b5a2afe437d747e6b0","tid":1804571,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"怕唔怕俾人read到ebanking 資料跟住偷錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f542dfa43121f4ae16a961b91b723384e8bccef","tid":1804571,"uid":261067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb951d1694f1d35aa300c2b5a2afe437d747e6b0","tid":1804571,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"怕唔怕俾人read到ebanking 資料跟住偷錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"唔怕架，因為你係登入左eBanking先開Macro Recorder。<br />\n同埋Macro Recorder係扮Mouse &amp; Keyboard Action，係唔會拿到你Login eBanking 的資料，比起之前PPS O個個機械人更安全啦。"},{"pid":"10dbc6e6e7abcd4348fc2a7902b80ece69e76351","tid":1804571,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763cd428921ea913dd277a100d42753a449eace7","tid":1804571,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T08:12:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db85dd34506a46d8673f4476de3338b0394b53e","tid":1804571,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:29:08.000Z","msg":"到底收支票蝕啲定用ebanking 蝕啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d234e8e1a1d3df1b7723ae29b2e4ee4a9c2de37d","tid":1804571,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc11151e1bf5810f8febb2e4975